######SNS service########
SNS service is one of the messaging service in AWS which is used to send email/sms notifications
to subscribers

Subscribers are connected with a topic which we create in SNS service

########Steps for SNS service#########
1. Goto sns
   create topic
   copy the arn number generated against topic
2. Goto subscriptions
   create subscription
      give arn obtained from topic
      protocol - email(sends email notification)
      endpoint - specify the email on which notifications to send
   we can create number of subscriptions
3. Notifications will be send to users
   Users have to confirm subscription in order to receive notifications
4. Topics - Publish -
   Create message
   Publish



